{"type":"message","id":"f307f572","parentId":"509c0f6a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:29:08.338Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Great! OpenClaw supports many chat platforms. Let me give a concise summary to 小八.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOpenClaw 支持超多聊天软件！🤩 目前文档里有的：\n\n| 类别 | 平台 |\n|------|------|\n| **主流 IM** | Telegram、WhatsApp、Discord、Slack、Signal |\n| **国内** | 飞书、微信（企业微信）、LINE |\n| **Apple** | iMessage、BlueBubbles |\n| **开源/去中心化** | Matrix、Nostr、IRC |\n| **办公协作** | Microsoft Teams、Google Chat、Mattermost、Nextcloud Talk、Synology Chat |\n| **其他** | Twitch、Zalo、Tlon |\n\n当前你已经接了 **飞书** 🦐\n\n想接入哪个？告诉我平台名，我帮你配置～"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":16798,"output":169,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16967,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775291345782,"responseId":"chatcmpl-81e443ae-d5d5-410e-9727-70046945673d"}}
